{"tid":716552,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"輸到生氣　韓國足協對墨西哥之戰「誤判」提出抗議","createTime":"2018-06-25T11:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T09:49:55.000Z","uid":109743,"like":82,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3a198194063beea61f51ea7fea6fab8774f0ec5b","tid":716552,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"韓國足球協會今（25）日宣布，將俄羅斯世足賽對墨西哥之戰的「誤判」向FIFA(國際足總）提出抗議，並對比賽結果表達遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n韓國隊備戰最後一場比賽，相關人士指出，「墨西哥拿下第2分前，我們看了之前的影片後，內部協商會議，奇誠庸選手被墨西哥球員奪球的過程中，的確有被犯規。」<br />\n<br />\n韓國隊提出的狀況是在對戰墨西哥下半場21分鐘左右，Javier Hern&aacute;ndez拿下第2分前發生，H&eacute;ctor Herrera 對奇誠庸展開干擾，韓國選手一瞬間有停止，但主審並未判犯規，因此墨西哥就開始反擊最後還進球，但主審並未判犯規。<br />\n<br />\n韓國足協表示：「主審在角度上也會有死角，由於攻擊陣營發生被犯規狀況，其他的副審應該都看得很清楚，所以我們將會發送遺憾聲明給FIFA。」<br />\n<br />\n不過韓國隊要有心理準備，因為根據過去經驗，很少有改判的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20180625/2777337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20180625%2F2777337&d=j%2Fmkz3xy8RAYDM2hWATdMTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6a8d3aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20180625/2777337</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重溫韓國2002 世界盃 黑哨!!!!!!!!! 體育黑暗史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/694538/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/694538/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"614e4879e9a700b61ba8139ddfae82a03cade866","tid":716552,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"報應"},{"pid":"3eb11e70bb321b8bee250d1daaf50c70f78be522","tid":716552,"uid":80527,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-2